              class="testimonial-img"
            /> -->
            <h4>John Doe</h4>
            <p>
              "This blog website has been a fantastic platform for sharing ideas and
              connecting with like-minded individuals. I highly recommend it!"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <!-- <img
              src="path-to-image/person2.jpg"
              alt="Person 2"
              class="testimonial-img"
            /> -->
            <h4>Jane Smith</h4>
            <p>
              "An excellent website for reading insightful posts on various topics.
              The user interface is modern and easy to navigate."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <!-- <img
              src="path-to-image/person3.jpg"
              alt="Person 3"
